body_html: I did a search on tensorflow for any zeros_initializer and ones_initializer instances that may have been missed and there are none. tflearn is not a tensorflow supported library so you should report those issues to the actual tflearn repo on github. Likewise, tensorflow_serving issues should be reported to the tensorflow_serving repo.
